latestPosts.caption:
HYROX ! What a day.

Had the opportunity to participate in HYROX this Saturday an incredible event, brilliantly organized and buzzing with energy. Huge shoutout to the entire team for putting it together.

It was even more special to see athletes from @flofitboxmumbai in action, representing with heart and hustle. Felt proud watching people fly in from all over the world to be part of it. The fitness scene in India is changing and fast. It’s inspiring to witness this movement grow.

I didn’t perform the way I hoped,pulled my calf badly during the sled push (second station), but chose to keep going. Quitting was never an option. “Keep going and cross the finish line with pride” my dad always said that. So I did.

Now… my calf may or may not be completely torn. We’ll find out soon enough! 🤣😆

The dream is pursuing, and we are coming to your cities!

We’re opening two more outlets and
stepping into the next chapter of growth.
We’re not just expanding, we’re evolving, with the same love for luxury and wellness.
New cities, same promise 💫

#FlorianHurelHairCoutureAndSpa #Hyderabad #Pune

latestPosts.caption:
#TBSTalks is bringing you an exclusive chat with the man who’s revolutionizing hair care, Florian Hurel! ✨

From Paris to Mumbai, this celebrity hairstylist turned entrepreneur is redefining what it means to care for your tresses. With his luxe brand, FHair, Florian’s vision is all about blending creativity with luxury—because hair care should feel as fabulous as a red carpet moment💇‍♂️💫

Florian’s journey from humble beginnings to global fame is as inspiring as his cuts. Tune in as he spills the tea on how FHair came to life, and what’s next in his mission to shake up the beauty world🔥

#TheBlendedStories #Mumbai #TBSTalks #FlorianHurel #FHair #HairGoals #CelebrityHairstylist #LuxuryHairCare

Celebrity hairstylist Florian Hurel (@florianhurel) has worked his magic on some of the most iconic names in Bollywood, but his latest ventures are just as headline-worthy.

With luxe salon spaces in Mumbai and the launch of his very own hair care line, FHair, Hurel is on a mission to make the Indian salon industry and hair care products a globally-recognised property through his endeavours. In this interview, he opens up about his entrepreneurial journey, the inspiration behind his products, and where he sees grooming trends heading next. Spoiler: it’s all about individuality, innovation, and everyday luxury. Head to the link in bio for more
